{Name}{}{Mynoc}
{DescAliveShort}{}{You see Mynoc}
{DescAliveFull}{}{A man in an Advanced Power Armor with a spear in his hand. He is waiting near the building entrance and is looking around. Maybe it is some kind of ceremonial guard.}
{Speech 1}{}{Преддиалоговые установки}
{Speech 1 Answer 23}{}{No familiar, nice-looking.}
{Speech 1 Answer 24}{}{Famiar, ugly.}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{Familiar, clever.}
{Speech 1 Answer 102}{}{Familiar, dumb.}
{Speech 2}{}{Hi, @pname@! Are you looking for something?}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{No, no... Just looking around.}
{Speech 2 Answer 6}{}{Yes, I need to ask you about something...}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{Hey, Mynoc. What's with your armor? It looks pretty rusty.}
{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{I've got some lubricant for your tin can.}
{Speech 2 Answer 5}{}{Hey, Mynoc, I guess I've changed my mind. I'm not looking for your lubricant anymore, don't count on me.}
{Speech 2 Answer 17}{}{I have dealed with those raiders, they are not going to rob any caravans anymore.}
{Speech 2 Answer 21}{}{Raiders are destroyed. You are safe now.}
{Speech 2 Answer 17*}{}{Raiders are destroyed. Caravans are safe now. [Try to lie]}
{Speech 2 Answer 20}{}{Look, I think I don't want to get involved in any mess with these raiders... You better find someone else.}
{Speech 3}{}{Yeah, that's true. Some lubricant and a proper cleaning would be useful.}
{Speech 3 Answer 6}{}{I need to ask you about something else.}
{Speech 3 Answer 6*}{}{I'll bring you some lubricant if I find any. And now I need to ask you about something else...}
{Speech 4}{}{Thanks, replicant. Here, take some money. Thanks again!}
{Speech 4 Answer 6}{}{No problem, mate. And now I need to ask you about something else...}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{You're welcome. And I need to go now.}
{Speech 5}{}{I didn't even ask you for that.}
{Speech 6}{}{What do you want to know?@@Go on, ask.@@What do you want to ask about?}
{Speech 6 Answer 7}{}{What a fancy armor you have here. Can you sell it to me?}
{Speech 6 Answer 7*}{}{Where did you get this armor?}
{Speech 6 Answer 11}{}{Hey, how did you guys manage to build such a city from nothing?}
{Speech 6 Answer 26}{}{What is it you doing? Are you guarding something?}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Nothing actually. Bye.}
{Speech 7}{}{It's not just an armor, it's a relict! It belonged to Chosen One himself!}
{Speech 7 Answer 9}{}{Chosen One? Who da hell is that?}
{Speech 7 Answer 8}{}{And why did he leave it? Where is he now?}
{Speech 7 Answer 3}{}{Chosen One? Yeah, it looks like it has been through lot.}
{Speech 8}{}{Are you kidding me? Noone knows. He helped us to build this city, he lived here with us, and then he simply dissapeared one day.}
{Speech 8 Answer 6}{}{Я хотел@sex@||а| бы спросить тебя ещё кое о чем.}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{I see... Well, thanks for the story, I need to go.}
{Speech 9}{}{Chosen One... He was the greatest of all people! Our brahmins were suffering from diseases, crops were dying from drought... It was a hard time in our life...}
{Speech 9 Answer 10}{}{[More]}
{Speech 10}{}{He managed to find G.E.C.K. and he helped us to restore the village... He saved both us and Vault dwellers. He saved many people from that scary Enclave. His name will be remembered forewer.}
{Speech 10 Answer 6}{}{I want to ask you about something else...}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit}{}{I see... Well, thanks for the story, I need to go.}
{Speech 11}{}{It's all thans to Chosen One. We survived only because of him...}
{Speech 11 Answer 10}{}{[More]}
{Speech 12}{}{Yes, I could use a guy like... no, not like you. Sorry. You look too unexperienced.}
{Speech 12 Answer 6}{}{Well... Ok. And not I want to ask about this...}
{Speech 13}{}{Actually, I could use some help, as we have a situation here, and I cannot leave the city...}
{Speech 13 Answer 14}{}{[More]}
{Speech 14}{}{Klamath caravans have ceised trade with us. I've heard a raider gang has set a camp somewhere on that side of the Canyon and they're attacking the traders.}
{Speech 14 Answer 15}{}{[More]}
{Speech 15}{}{They are not attacking the city itself, but we need someone to help us deal with them. Can you see if you can do anything?}
{Speech 15 Answer 16}{}{Okay, I'll try. Not for free, or course.}
{Speech 15 Answer Exit}{}{Emm... Sorry, I forgot I have an appointment right now, I have to go, bye!}
{Speech 15 Answer 16*}{}{It would be a pleasure! Just tell me where to search for them!}
{Speech 16}{}{Great! I'll mark an approximate location on your map. And hurry up! They are not going to wait there forever!}
{Speech 17}{}{Excellent! But I was just told that main forces were outside the camp... One caravaner told us where we could find them.}
{Speech 17 Answer 20}{}{Hey, just give me my money, dealing with any 'main forces' was not a part of agreement.}
{Speech 17 Answer 18}{}{I'll crack them. Where to go?}
{Speech 18}{}{I'll mark the location on your map, just give me your Pip-Boy... Done. Here's your money for the first part and you can also have something from the equipment - you could use a good gun in a next fight.}
{Speech 18 Answer 16}{}{Give me a cattle prod. I grew up in a farm and I'm used to this weapon.}
{Speech 18 Answer 16*}{}{I'll take a laser pistol.}
{Speech 18 Answer 16**}{}{A power fist would be cool. Enjoy crashing jaws with it.}
{Speech 18 Answer 16***}{}{AK-112, an assault rifle. I'm not playing toys.}
